Name:                   cuda
Version:                0.1
Synopsis:               A binding to the "C for CUDA" interface for programming NVIDIA GPUs
Description:    
    A binding to the "C for CUDA" interface for programming NVIDIA GPUs
    .
    The CUDA library provides a direct, general purpose SPMD programming model
    for NVIDIA graphics cards (G8x series onwards).

